{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_10_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 内緒です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――特番翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Day After the Special",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あけましておめでとう、瑠依。今年もよろしくな\n昨日は特番の後、ゆっくり休めたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year‚ Rui. Looking forward to another year with you.\nWere you able to rest properly after the special yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あけましておめでとうございます\n……って、ご挨拶は昨日もしましたけどね。ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year.\n…Though we already said that yesterday. Fufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3681078664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は寮に帰ってから、倒れるように寝てしまいました\n完全なオフだから、気兼ねなく眠れた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I collapsed into bed as soon as I got back to the dorm.\nSince it was a full day off‚ I slept without a care.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、私達の初詣に付き合ってくださるんですよね\nとてもありがたいんですけど……ただ、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re coming with us for our first shrine visit today‚ right?\nI’m very grateful‚ but… um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、来たのは瑠依だけか？\n優とすみれは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Is it just you‚ Rui?\nWhere are Yu and Sumire…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "実は……「どうしても故郷のお雑煮が食べたい」と\n急に二人が言い出して……料理を始めてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… they suddenly said they had to eat\ntheir hometown-style ozoni‚ and ended up starting to cook.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく、ボディーガード役で来てくれる\nという話だったのに……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you kindly agreed to come\nas our bodyguard… I’m really sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5670290869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルだけで初詣は、さすがに心配だしな\nでも、二人とも随分急だな。日を改めた方がいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be worrying for idols to go alone.\nStill‚ that’s sudden. Should we reschedule?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.788644554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはさすがに悪いです！　その……二人はきっと\n後から合流しますから……行きましょう、初詣！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ that would be too much trouble! Um…\nThey’ll surely join us later… Let’s go to the shrine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.076504331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ちょうどお昼時ですから\n私達も、何か食べながら待っていてもいいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it’s just about lunchtime‚\nso we could eat something while we wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666618347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。じゃあ、そうしようか\nとはいえ、外の店はどこも混んでるか休みだしな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. Let’s do that.\nThough everywhere outside is either crowded or closed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3666618347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、カップ麺にしませんか？\nこの間はおうどんだったので、おそばも食べてみたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then how about cup noodles?\nI had udon last time‚ so I’d like to try soba too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "カップ麺？\n確かに、まだまだ事務所に残ってるが、いいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cup noodles?\nWe do still have plenty at the office‚ but is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "はい。この間のCMでも「年明けも、うどんとおそばで\nおめでコン！」っていうセリフがありましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. In the recent CM‚ there was the line—\n“New Year KONgratulations with udon and soba!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.799995168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、美味しかった。おそばの風味がしっかりしていて\nそれに、かき揚げもさくさくでした……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ that was delicious. The soba flavor was rich‚\nand the fried tofu was perfectly crispy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9666618347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うどんの方もうまかったよ。麺にコシがあって、出汁の\n染みた油揚げが最高だった。瑠依が言っていた通りだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The udon was great too. The noodles were springy‚\nand the broth-soaked tofu was amazing. Just like you said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私が言ったこと、覚えてくれていたんですね\nふふっ……なんだか嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You remembered what I said.\nFufu… that makes me happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.26056098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……今日のテレビ、お正月の番組一色ですね\n新年の番組って、なんだか特別な空気を感じます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it… TV today is all New Year programs.\nNew Year’s shows have such a special atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5666618347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "いつ点けても、まるでお祭りみたいな感じがして……\n私、子供の頃、この雰囲気が好きでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter when you turn it on‚ it feels like a festival…\nI loved this feeling when I was a child.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5631376778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "世間は正月で静かなのに、テレビの中はお祭りムードで\nそのコントラストが、これぞ正月って感じだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The world is quiet for New Year‚ but TV is festive.\nThat contrast really feels like New Year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "今では私も、そんなお祭りの中の一人なんですね\nあ……！　今流れてる、このCM……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ I’m part of that festival myself.\nAh…! This CM that’s on right now…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1260364707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうどさっき話していた、カップ麺のCMですね\n新春らしい雰囲気で、晴れやかな気持ちになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the cup noodle CM we were just talking about.\nIt feels so New Year-like—bright and refreshing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2333285014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "こうして見ると、狐の耳、意外と自然ですね\nCMの内容も、綺麗なセットもお正月らしいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing it now‚ the fox ears look surprisingly natural.\nThe content of the CM and the beautiful set both really feel New Year-like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n私、新年のお祭り感を、ちゃんと出せていますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nAm I properly conveying that New Year festival feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.3201186225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、もちろん。このCMを観ていると\n新春らしい、わくわくした気持ちになるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Watching this commercial\nreally gives me that fresh New Year excitement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.9666699726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "いつも忙しい{user}さんにも\n新春らしさと、わくわくを届けられたなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’ve managed to bring that fresh New Year feeling\nand excitement to you‚ even though you’re always so busy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.853787935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "撮影での努力が、報われた気がします\n頑張って、良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I feel like my effort during filming paid off.\nI’m glad I worked hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.8666486103,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3159.473808900003,
          "startTime": 221.0261224192
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5986.684977300001,
          "startTime": 223.8533335876
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、優とすみれからメッセが届きました\n遅れるから、先に二人で初詣に行ってて、だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ I got a message from Yu and Sumire.\nThey said they’ll be late‚ so we should go to the shrine just the two of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.3405264454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ、あの二人は。せっかく{user}さん\nが付き合ってくれるっていうのに、失礼です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ those two… It’s really rude‚\nespecially when you were kind enough to come with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.5666384378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺は気にしてないよ。それに年に一度の正月だ\n少しくらい、自由に過ごしてもいいと思うしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind. And it’s New Year—once a year.\nIt’s fine to enjoy a little freedom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.9999717711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_03-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがそう言ってくださるなら\nいいんですけど……一応、二人に後で言っておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so then it’s fine…\nthough I’ll mention it to them later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.5999717711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
