      "text": "{user}さん、随分長く手を合わせて\nいましたけど、どんなお願いごとをしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you were praying for quite a long time.\nWhat kind of wish did you make?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.5666628519,
