      "text": "星見プロのみんなが、今年も一年、大きな怪我もなく\n活躍出来ますように、って。そういう瑠依は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wishing that everyone at Hoshimi Pro stays safe\nand keep doing well. How about you‚ Rui?",
