      "text": "私は、「去年は新しいことに沢山挑戦出来ました」\nというご報告と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told them‚ “Last year‚ I was able to try many new things.”\nThat was my report—and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.1333295185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
